    This class helps to implement a unified set of client support commands that translate between client support requests and core GNS commands that are sent to the server. Specifically the CommandModule class maintains the list of commands, mechanisms for looking up commands from the contents of JSONObject encoded command packets as well as supporting generation of command documentation.
